{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a7d856f9-086d-4f19-91c9-669be1adb8ed","content":"No repo-specific pipeline files here, so this is a general guidance question. Here's how to migrate:\n\n### 1. Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a script)\n\n```yaml\n# Before (VSTest)\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    runSettingsFile: test.runsettings\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After (Microsoft.Testing.Platform)\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 2. Enable Microsoft.Testing.Platform in your test projects\n\nIn each test `.csproj`, add:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nOr set `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` to keep using `dotnet test` as the entry point.\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest   # TRX format\n    testResultsFiles: '**/results.trx'\n  condition: always()\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key differences from VSTest@3\n\n| Concern | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Runner | `vstest.console.exe` | `dotnet test` / native exe |\n| TRX output | Built-in | `--logger trx` |\n| Code coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Test discovery | DLL glob | Project/solution reference |\n\nNo changes are needed for your `.runsettings` file—pass it via `-- --settings test.runsettings` if needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"9073636d-46a6-4be2-92e6-18ecfa4c872b","outputTokens":558,"requestId":"CFE6:21A8FE:61A1A1E:6CCF0EB:69EC0EA8"},"id":"f3dbd1dc-6b51-415f-a8e8-37b48c4e9a12","timestamp":"2026-04-25T00:45:39.366Z","parentId":"3cff71b1-7541-4d1d-83f3-c88ce63397d0"}
